Papers that informed the broader project but don't directly support
claims in this paper:

- RBJ: Performance of Low-Order Polynomial Interpolators
- RBJ: Effect of DAC Deglitching on Frequency Response
- RBJ: Comments on Time-Delay Spectrometry
- Julius O. Smith III: Introduction to Digital Filters (CCRMA)
- Julius O. Smith III: Audio Signal Processing in MATLAB
- Christiansen: full citation note (pending [17] confirmation)
- Zavalishin: note pointing to full book beyond what §2.2 cites

Keeps numbered references clean while acknowledging the full
scope of DSP literature that shaped the project.
